OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776380581
OL,3,CEasyJet issues profits warning as
OL,4,Ceconomic impact of war intensifies
OL,6,FThe government has pinned its fortunes
OL,7,Fon an economic revival that has yet to
OL,8,Fhappen - but in February, there were
OL,9,Fsparks of life.
OL,11,FThe UK economy grew by 0.5% - far
OL,12,Foutpacing expectations.
OL,14,FWe'll never know what would have
OL,15,Fhappened next, as on February 27,
OL,16,Feverything changed.
OL,18,FThere are clear signs that the war in
OL,19,FIran has caused households here to
OL,20,Frein in spending and businesses to
OL,21,Fdelay investment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
