OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776380581
OL,3,CEasyJet issues profits warning as
OL,4,Ceconomic impact of war intensifies
OL,6,F"This will likely be the growth before
OL,7,Fthe energy squeeze," says Sanjay Raja,
OL,8,FChief UK Economist at Deutsche Bank.
OL,9,F"Pump prices are up over 20% since the
OL,10,Foil shock occurred. And dual-fuel
OL,11,Fbills are due to rise by a similar
OL,12,Famount over the summer."
OL,14,FThis morning, easyJet warned of
OL,15,Fwidening losses. The price of jet fuel
OL,16,Fhas doubled since the conflict began,
OL,17,Fcosting the airline #25 million in
OL,18,FMarch alone.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@TO]qD@AOUtD@XO]
