OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776380581
OL,3,CEasyJet issues profits warning as
OL,4,Ceconomic impact of war intensifies
OL,6,FThe chief executive said passengers
OL,7,Fwere holding off on summer bookings
OL,8,Famid the uncertainty.
OL,10,FToday, the International Energy Agency
OL,11,Fwarned that Europe has "maybe six
OL,12,Fweeks or so of jet fuel left", raising
OL,13,Fthe prospect that airlines may soon
OL,14,Fhave to start cancelling flights.
OL,16,FEasyJet's Kenton Jarvis says he has
OL,17,F"no concerns" about supplies for the
OL,18,Fnext "three to four weeks" and urged
OL,19,Fpassengers to "book early" to avoid
OL,20,Fhigher fares.
