OL,3,CEasyJet issues profits warning as
OL,4,Ceconomic impact of war intensifies
OL,6,FConcerns about availability extend to
OL,7,Fother commodities, such as carbon
OL,8,Fdioxide, which is widely used in food
OL,9,Fproduction.
OL,11,FThe government says it is working on
OL,12,Fcontingency plans to avoid gaps on
OL,13,Fshelves.
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
