OL,3,CEasyJet issues profits warning as
OL,4,Ceconomic impact of war intensifies
OL,6,FTesco reported its results this
OL,7,Fmorning. The supermarket's boss, Ken
OL,8,FMurphy, said there are no issues with
OL,9,Fdeliveries currently, and none of the
OL,10,Fcompany's "growers, suppliers or food
OL,11,Fmanufacturers have flagged any risk".
OL,13,FThere are, however, warnings on
OL,14,Fprices. The Food and Drink Federation
OL,15,Fbelieves food inflation could hit 9%
OL,16,Fby the end of the year.
OL,18,FMurphy is dismissive, although he
OL,19,Fdeclined to give a figure he considers
OL,20,Fmore realistic.
OL,26,@rD@KOUsD@dO]
