OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776380581
OL,3,CEasyJet issues profits warning as
OL,4,Ceconomic impact of war intensifies
OL,6,FHe said the war had created a "very
OL,7,Fvolatile, unpredictable" situation,
OL,8,Fbut that the business has not yet
OL,9,Fexperienced any meaningful rise in
OL,10,Finflation.
OL,12,FHe added: "I'm in my sixth year in
OL,13,Fthis job and it's, I think, my sixth
OL,14,Fcrisis."
OL,16,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,17,Four political experts are across all
OL,18,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,19,Fto the latest episode below...
